e":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T01:10:24.000Z","msg":"其實兔本身就好脆弱 半年前既body check結果根本代表唔到任何野 <br />\n<br />\n不過剪毛個單都反映左呢間野係咩態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T01:13:29.000Z","msg":"如果冇信心照顧得好，咪唔好做兔仔生意<br />\n做貓狗囉<br />\n<br />\n我冇養過兔仔，但覺得咁樣糟質主人當係寶的寵物，有冇再仆街啲呀"},{"pid":"145e19192c88a9f9e72800fd2e484bedddad1bbc","tid":1119337,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"994429888d0e5ff585092e5cff07629f4967a4a7","tid":1119337,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T00:42:14.000Z","msg":"睇到心都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}